lead_paragraph: Ferrari's Sebastian Vettel has escaped sanction after apologising to Formula One race director Charlie Whiting and the sport's governing body for Sunday's expletive-laden Mexican Grand Prix rant.

headline.print_headline: Sweary Vettel Escapes FIA Sanction After Apology
